remove_liquidity(uint256,uint256[2]).details: Withdrawal amounts are based on current deposit ratios

params._min_underlying_amounts: Minimum amounts of underlying coins to receive

returns._0: List of amounts of underlying coins that were withdrawn

params._underlying_amounts: List of amounts of underlying coins to withdraw

returns._0: List of amounts of underlying coins that were withdrawn

params._amount: Amount of LP tokens to burn in the withdrawal
params._min_underlying_amount: Minimum amount of underlying coin to receive
params.i: Index value of the coin to withdraw
